org.apache.river.extra.discovery

Class MulticastServiceFinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.river.extra.discovery.MulticastServiceFinder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ServiceFinder

    public class MulticastServiceFinder
extends Object
implements ServiceFinder
    Implementation which uses multicast to find all the lookup services in the local subnet. Discovery of new/replacement services is then handed to the internal ServiceDiscoveryManager.
